{
  "stem": "17374.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was just order.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think it was '41 or something like that, '41 I believe [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe eight months is all.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Well, we [? used to ?] have a good time [? nothing, ?] like, like you do on holiday in country.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went-- that first time, they taught me how to swim.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a little river up there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I went for the river, and we had-- [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that Polish boy that thought I was-- [POLISH] was his name.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was a real peasant.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when come that harvest, he was-- with the blade, he was cutting this wheat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was wheat, and corn, and everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that Jewish boy was so handsome.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was flirt, and he was gorgeous.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And even my sister was laughing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Always, they fight about me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] That was terrific time, yeah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But it was very short time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We go to ghetto.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Cracow-- it was in [POLISH], that again suburb of Cracow, [? right? ?] And it was already frightening for me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was very frightening, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Which?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not, not directly to me, but we knew that come order to go to ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I don't know who was the one.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was order, don't know, not directly to me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that was [? the decision. ?] Some people did go further.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we found out they all perished.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They went to ?] [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Auschwitz, ?] [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we went to ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was a-- oh, you want to know about ghetto?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "How did you get from Tonie to the ghetto?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Again, with the horse and buggy, and something like this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All family, some of the family-- for instance, [?",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
